Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:33.00,CreditInfo,,0,0,0,,\N制作信息\N翻译：AI女孩小雪（https://github.com/SnowAIGirl）\N时间轴：基于 Crunchyroll 官方字幕\N语音识别：faster-whisper（日语→中文直译）\N\N本字幕仅供学习交流，请勿用于商业用途。如侵权请联系删除。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:41.79,Default,OHNO,0,0,0,,哎呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:45.13,Default,OHNO,0,0,0,,山田酱真努力啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:48.38,Default,OHNO,0,0,0,,我得向你学习。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:51.47,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,大野小姐的笑容已经很完美了。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:52.97,Default,OHNO,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.39,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,山田。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:57.76,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,能请你拍个照做个采访吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:00.98,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,什么？又是公司宣传？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:03.14,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,至少把不情愿藏起来啊山田。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:06.40,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我之前不是刚做过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:08.27,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,没办法。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:11.32,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,你今年又入围微笑奖了。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:12.65,Default,OHNO,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:14.45,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,好吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:16.66,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,赶紧搞完吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:19.33,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,转变真快。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:22.54,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,我都有点怀念你兼职时没笑脸的样子了。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:28.29,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b0\fnNoto Sans SC\bord2\fs40\c&H080907&\3c&H080907&\t(17,1025,\3c&HFFFFFF&)\pos(335,95)}8 Years Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:28.29,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs22\shad2\bord1\fnArial Black\c&H080907&\3c&H080907&\4c&H080907&\t(17,1025,\c&H6EA178&\3c&HE2F4E7&\4c&H637468&)\frz3.84\fax-0.1\pos(78.5,251)}Superfresh Market
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:30.80,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.46,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,欢迎光临。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:33.55,Flashback,GOTOU,0,0,0,,真差劲！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:37.22,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,到底哪里不对店长？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:39.85,Flashback,GOTOU,0,0,0,,眼神死板的嘴在抽搐。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:40.81,Flashback,GOTOU,0,0,0,,声音也太小。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:44.06,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,被你说得好像我全错了。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:46.31,Flashback,GOTOU,0,0,0,,你明白就好。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:49.61,Flashback,GOTOU,0,0,0,,怎么教你才能做好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:52.40,Flashback,GOTOU,0,0,0,,其他工作都完美为什么就这个不行。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:54.07,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,一点也不完美。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:58.03,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我还会被投诉服务态度。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:02.33,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,总是给你添麻烦对不起。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.54,Flashback,GOTOU,0,0,0,,听着山田。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:12.09,Flashback,GOTOU,0,0,0,,投诉你的都是同一个针对你的顾客。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:16.09,Flashback,GOTOU,0,0,0,,他们就是想找茬拿你当借口。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:19.97,Flashback,GOTOU,0,0,0,,投诉和你的服务我都会想办法。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:22.22,Flashback,GOTOU,0,0,0,,你别多想继续做好就行。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:24.98,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.60,FlashbackItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,店长对我真好。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:32.48,FlashbackItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,虽然，我给她添了这么多麻烦。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:38.91,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,拿到服务台可以换优惠券。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:41.16,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,拿到服务台可以换优惠券。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:43.70,Flashback,LADY,0,0,0,,哦是这样啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.62,Flashback,LADY,0,0,0,,谢谢小姐。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.37,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,感谢您——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:54.46,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:58.68,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,欢迎光临。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:00.01,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,积分卡——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.10,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,我像带了吗？当然是忘了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:05.93,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,非常抱歉。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:09.06,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,需要袋子——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:11.44,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,你看篮子里有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:12.82,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,那就是需要。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:17.57,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,要说几次你才能记住。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:20.78,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,您说得对对不起。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:23.45,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我知道了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:24.58,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:28.83,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,为什么先扫鸡蛋？压碎了怎么办？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:31.25,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,这是基本常识吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.34,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,你上司什么都没教你吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.71,FlashbackTop,CUSTOMER 1,0,0,0,,那边怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:31.83,FlashbackTop,CUSTOMER 2,0,0,0,,看起来不妙。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:37.09,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,其他收银员也跟你一样吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.09,Flashback,OHNO,0,0,0,,店长！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.93,Flashback,OHNO,0,0,0,,后藤店长！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:43.60,Flashback,OHNO,0,0,0,,那个顾客又来了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:45.26,Flashback,OHNO,0,0,0,,山田酱在被骂！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:50.14,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,每次结账你都一脸不情愿。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:52.98,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,你为什么要在这里工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.69,FlashbackTop,MOTHER,0,0,0,,别听他的。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:56.86,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,你怎么不说话？道歉呢？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.44,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,非常抱歉。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.61,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,又是这一句！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:03.24,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,至少道歉要像真心的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.87,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,所以，我讨厌学生工服务！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:08.41,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,旁边便利店那个也不行。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.54,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,你更差劲！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.63,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,我教你你还不听——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:14.75,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,喂。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:17.76,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,打扰一下。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.72,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,能闭嘴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.22,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,什、什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:30.10,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,没看到我在训这个不称职的收银员吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.27,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦呃……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.98,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯我听得很清楚。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:39.32,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,但你中途开始扯不相干的话了。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:43.41,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,而且，你不是老来骂这个姑娘吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.53,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,能不能消停会儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:50.83,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,这里还有其他收银台。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:50.83,FlashbackTop,KID,0,0,0,,上啊大叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.92,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你为什么非要……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.63,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,每次我排队都这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:06.68,Flashback,MANAGER,0,0,0,,先生请跟我们走一趟。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:07.89,Flashback,NITPICKER,0,0,0,,啧。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.56,Flashback,GOTOU,0,0,0,,让大野小姐接班。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:16.73,Flashback,OHNO,0,0,0,,你休息一下亲爱的。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.69,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,好的。
