Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:46.51,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:50.01,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,啊是你。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:53.73,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,谢谢你刚才帮我解围。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:57.31,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,而且，让你因为我等了那么多次对不起。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.19,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,等等不对。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:02.23,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那不全是你的错。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:05.65,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,不全是我的错，因为我服务不好。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.53,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,所以，对不起。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:16.37,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我帮你不是为了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:24.51,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,只是今天工作遇到糟心事正烦着。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:28.09,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,又看到你在挨骂。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:37.64,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,连那个一直对我很好的收银员都要挨骂。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.44,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我就火了才插嘴的。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:42.19,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我对你很好？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:45.57,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯又快又仔细。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:49.28,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,你对一个不在意的不礼貌的兼职这么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:51.78,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你不在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.79,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你明明一直全力以赴。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.54,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(143,1)\fs15\u1\fnComic Sans MS\bord2\c&H363636&\3c&HF5F6F9&\frz-11.57\fax-0.1\pos(270.5,69.5)}Always start with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:03.05,FlashbackItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,至少得快。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.47,FlashbackItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,为什么我做不对呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:18.81,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,等等你……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:25.36,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对、对不起我说了什么让你哭了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:26.69,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我没哭。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:29.82,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,只是眼睛在出汗。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:30.95,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,出汗……？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:35.74,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我一直在努力。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:38.16,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我服务那么差。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:42.71,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,被难缠的顾客盯上。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:46.38,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,给同事和店长添那么多麻烦……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:53.14,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我想改好！我喜欢这份工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.47,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,好难受……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:59.81,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你喜欢这份工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.65,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那就没问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:12.07,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,因为，喜欢而坚持下去。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:16.74,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,其他需要的自然会来。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.30,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯？你、你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.51,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,是那个。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:35.80,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,你的烟熏到我眼睛了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.51,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对、对不起拿太近了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:38.47,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,噗。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:40.39,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,等等又怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.52,Flashback,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:45.86,Flashback,YAMADA,0,0,0,,你的反应都太夸张了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.83,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,好了应该够了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:59.29,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,采访结束。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.58,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,你可以休息了。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.25,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,喂店长。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.96,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,这家店还叫另一个名字的时候。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:10.55,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,有个人帮我骂过一个针对我的顾客。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:11.67,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:17.18,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,我干了这么多年见过多少个这样的了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:19.14,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,不可能完全不记得。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:23.81,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,连我也不记得他的脸了。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:29.32,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,他总是在店里买完东西在门口抽烟。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:33.11,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,头发乱蓬蓬衬衫皱巴巴。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.41,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,黑眼圈很重。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:45.71,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我们因为投诉撤掉烟灰缸后他就不再来了。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:52.09,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,不知道他现在在哪里抽着呢？
